{
  "id": "adv_event_2303_01_01",
  "title": "終わらない\n宿題",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "ここは、この方程式を使って……うん、解けた！\nこれで春休みの宿題はおしまいっと！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Here‚ using this equation… Yup‚ got it!\nWith this‚ I'm done with my spring break homework!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.9999999881,
      "endTime": 13.852449214499998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "早いですわね！？　私は全然終わっていないのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That was fast‚ huh!? I'm not even close to done…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.0666666548,
      "endTime": 19.2073243658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "勉強するふりして、お喋りしたり\nお菓子食べたりしてるからですよ。もぐもぐ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's because you pretend to study but chat instead‚\nand munch on snacks‚ see? munch munch",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.4139908989,
      "endTime": 27.128525944499998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "そんなんじゃ勉強が進む訳ないです、ぱりぽり\nあ、このポテトチップス美味しいです～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You won't make progress like that‚ crunch crunch\nOh‚ these potato chips are good~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.3285258491,
      "endTime": 35.0191379745,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "正論ですが、お菓子を食べてばかりのあなたに\n言われると、なんだか無性に腹が立ちますわね！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's true‚ but coming from someone who just eats chips all the time‚\nit makes me unreasonably angry‚ doesn't it!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.2258046031,
      "endTime": 42.565531814100005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "ほらほら、早くしないと終わらないよ～\nせっかく中学生同士で勉強会を開いたんだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ hurry up or we won't finish!\nWe organized this study session among middle school students‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.7721986334,
      "endTime": 50.487278227000004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルだからって、ううん、アイドルだからこそ\n学業をおろそかにしちゃダメなんだよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and we're idols‚ but no‚ precisely because we're idols\nwe can't neglect our studies‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.6721986334,
      "endTime": 58.5979811232,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "私達の成績が下がったら、両親が心配しちゃうし\n活動を制限されちゃうかもしれないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If our grades drop‚ our parents will worry‚ and\nwe might even get restricted from activities.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.8055319667,
      "endTime": 65.9912917972,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "反論の余地がありませんわ……すみれは立派ですわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's no room for argument… Sumire is impressive",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.2055319667,
      "endTime": 71.71439808609999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、偉そうに言ってはみたけど\n実はぜーんぶ、瑠依ちゃんの受け売りなの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hahaha‚ I sounded so arrogant‚\nbut actually‚ it's all just what Rui-chan said",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.9210646193,
      "endTime": 78.9045568029,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "いえいえ、年はほとんど変わらないのに大したものです\nこのプロ意識は見習うべきですよ。ばりぼり",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh no‚ we're pretty much the same age‚ but that's impressive.\nThis level of professionalism is worth emulating‚ crunch crunch.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.1210646193,
      "endTime": 89.0919487518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "……そう思うのでしたら\nまずお菓子を食べるのをストップなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…If you really think so‚\nthen stop eating chips first",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.291948561,
      "endTime": 94.26460175919999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "まあまあ。ところでこのポテトチップス\n美味しいですよ？　ささ、すずにゃんもひと口",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh come on. By the way‚ these potato chips\nare too good‚ you know? Come on‚ Suzu-nyan‚ have a bite!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.471268483,
      "endTime": 101.5221754273,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "まったくあなたという人は……\nう～ん、とっても美味！　もう一枚！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're just…\nHmm‚ it's so delicious! Another piece!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.7288420559,
      "endTime": 110.2402935864,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、みんなのコップが空だ。飲み物取ってくるね\nその間、宿題サボっちゃダメだよ～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Oh‚ everyone's cups are empty. I'll get some drinks\nIn the meantime‚ don't slack off on your homework‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.4336267671,
      "endTime": 119.6109279833,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はぁーい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.8002934338,
      "endTime": 121.33333255849999,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3057.414464200008
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.607707898
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "（二人が宿題をちゃーんと終わらせられるように）\n（私がしっかりしないと。頑張るぞ！　……あれ？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（So they can finish their homework properly‚）\n（I need to be responsible. I'll do my best! …Huh?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.5243765992,
      "endTime": 132.8772568864,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.9910371623
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01-stm001.m4a",
      "text": "……奥山さん？\nこんにちは！　今日は何をしてるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Okuyama-san?\nHello! What are you doing today?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.4333272179,
      "endTime": 141.0333363851,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.9333363851
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 141.2589076044
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "事務所をお借りして、中学生組で勉強会です！\n春休みの宿題が溜まっちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We borrowed the office and are having a study session with the middle school students!\nOur spring break homework piled up…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.2589076044,
      "endTime": 147.77974662789998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.9922409377
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "さとみさんこそ、こんな所で窓の外を見つめて\nどうしたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Satomi-san‚ why are you staring out the window like that?\nWhat's wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.9922409377,
      "endTime": 153.84986003260002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.0589076044
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01-stm002.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、実は私も宿題が終わらなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha‚ actually‚ I haven't finished my homework either…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.0589076044,
      "endTime": 158.994780636,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 159.2347846193
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "宿題って、大人になってもあるんですね\nさとみさんの宿題はどんなのですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even adults have homework‚ huh?\nWhat kind of homework do you have‚ Satomi-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.2347846193,
      "endTime": 166.41115647979998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 166.6014512859
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01-stm003.m4a",
      "text": "それがですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ you see…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.6014512859,
      "endTime": 169.14081633909998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 170.3461537403
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "新しいアイドルユニットの、立ち上げ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Starting a new idol unit?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.3874718112,
      "endTime": 174.4263607902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 174.6208051445
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01-stm004.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんです。{user}さんに\nやってみないかって言われて",
      "translations": {
