    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "極限まで研ぎ澄まされたこころの嗅覚が\nチャンスの匂いを嗅ぎつけたのです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This sharpened sense of Kokoro‚ honed to the extreme‚\nhas caught the scent of opportunity",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 314.8609337569,
      "endTime": 320.59993579390004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 320.8066022317
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01-smr020.m4a",
      "text": "……二人とも、宿題サボっちゃダメって言ったよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But didn't we say not to neglect our homework?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 320.8066022317,
      "endTime": 325.6970329682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 325.9066022317
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それは……ほら！　すみれも言っていたでしょう！\n困った時は、助け合うのが仲間というものでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-That's… See! Sumire also said it‚ right?!\nWhen you're in trouble‚ helping each other is what mates are for‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 325.9066022317,
      "endTime": 334.8021127145,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 335.0087792476
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
