      "text": "う、うん……それはそうだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yeah… that's true‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 335.0087792476,
      "endTime": 338.958779343,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 339.1754459143
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "だからこころ達は、宿題という名の犠牲を払って\nさとみさんを救うため集まった、という訳なのです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So Kokoro and the others gathered‚\nsacrificing their homework‚ to save Satomi-san",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 339.1754459143,
      "endTime": 347.3048788786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_01-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "それに、みんなで意見を出し合った方が\n早く答えが見つかるかもしれませんわよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ sharing opinions together might\nlead to finding answers more quickly‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 347.5048786879,
      "endTime": 353.5981211424,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
