      "text": "そうですわ！　雫も呼ぶのはいかがです？\n雫のアイドルの知識は、きっと参考になりますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right! How about calling Shizuku too?\nHer knowledge about idols might be helpful!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 353.7847879808,
      "endTime": 361.35612596690004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
