      "text": "……うん、そうだね。ありがとう、二人とも！\n改めてさとみさん、私達にお手伝いさせて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah‚ that's a good idea. Thank you‚ both of you!\nOnce again‚ Satomi-san‚ please let us help you!",
        "id": ""
      },
